			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1. Recruit Karlach as companion using the debug book.\r\n2. In the origin debug book: Karlach --> Act 3 --> Gortash Confrontation --> Teleport to Audience Hall.\r\n3. Start ceremony with Karlach nearby. Let her attack Gortash so she is sent to prison.\r\n4. After the scene in the origin debug book: Karlach --> Act 3 --> Gortash Confrontation --> Teleport to prison.\r\n5. Free her, recruit her back and let her be spotted by a guard."
				},
